Darkangel returned to the base with the bot he found. He placed the bot in a CR tank. He would check on him in a while.

DeathStar also arrived back at base. Just before landing there had been traces of an incoming comm message but the jammers were still in place.

Both bots arrive at Tyrael&#39;s location.

Darkangel: Darkangel, reporting. The Maximals have defended themselves. Unicron&#39;s minions have been destroyed. Rodimus has agreed to the alliance. They are preparing. Also, I dound a crashed bot on the way back. He is currently in the CR tank.

DeathStar: The platform for the weapon has been constructed, sir.

